    <main class="px-3">
      <h1>Show your work photos.<i class="fas fa-camera-retro"></i></h1>
      <p class="lead">This application gives an opportunity create an album, add in it your work photos, share the
        album's link with your clients to know what photos <i class="fas fa-photo-video"></i> they have liked.</p>
      <div class="button-group">
        <button class="login btn btn-lg fw-bold border-white bg-white">Login</button>
        <button class="signUp btn btn-lg fw-bold border-white bg-white">Sign up</button>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
